# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Client env (Expo inlines EXPO_PUBLIC_* into the bundle — public by design)
# Copy to .env and fill in. With these unset, the app runs in offline demo
# mode (full core loop works, no account/API needed).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
EXPO_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Server secrets — NEVER put these in this file's EXPO_PUBLIC_ section or
# anywhere in the client. Set them as Supabase Edge Function secrets:
#
#   supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#   supabase secrets set STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
#   supabase secrets set STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
#   supabase secrets set STRIPE_PRICE_PLUS=price_...
#   supabase secrets set STRIPE_PRICE_PRO=price_...
#   supabase secrets set CHECKOUT_RETURN_URL=https://your-site/checkout-done
#
# (SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are provided
# to Edge Functions automatically by Supabase.)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
